# ServiceNow Agent - Git Ignore

# Node modules
node_modules/

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# OS Files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp
~$*

# Personal files (não compartilhar)
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.pdf
*.mov
*.jpeg
*.jpg
*.png
*.webp
*.zip
*.csv
*.json
SoapUI*

# Keep only agent files
!refinements/*.md
!examples/*.md